Something I’ve learned this year! If you can not see the light outside of yourself; YOU must be the Light! Own that shit. Yes it can be taxing to your energy. But Surround yourself with those who give you reciprocity. Love those who rejuvenate you &  Love you unconditionally! Those are your people! 2022 I lost, so gained, I cried, I loved, I danced, I cooked, I booked shows, I hosted, Most importantly I as I grow older I’m growing wiser. Kicking my anxieties ass! Thank you to all my friends & family for loving me in ways I couldn’t love myself. Thank y’all! Thank you! Y’all my tribe really really hold me down. I really feel so much love. I am full of gratitude. 🫶🏾 As we go into the unknown. I’m praying we all find love & peace.
